{
  "texts": [
    "Estimates from OLS models.",
    "In Panel A, the sample in Columns 1 and 2 is at the participant-round level (5 participants × 1400 rounds).",
    "The sample in Column 3 is at the group-round level (1400 rounds).",
    "Individual payoff = participant-level round payoffs in Canadian dollars; I(Individual found max):0/1=1 if the location of the maximum was found by the participant; I(Group found max):0/1=1 if the location of the maximum was found by at least one participant in the round.",
    "The excluded category captured by the constant is the condition without data."
  ]
}